g.aria-label: U.S ARMY MODEL B-17-10-BO AIR CORPS SERIAL NO. 4124485 CREW WEIGHT 1800 LBS.

THE FAMOUS "MEMPHIS BELLE", B-17-10-BO (N/S 41-24485), FUSELAGE MARKINGS "DF A" OF 324 BOMBER SQUADRON / 91 BOMBER GROUP, UNDER COMMAND OF CAPT. ROBERT MORGAN, IT WAS THE FIRST FLYNG FORTRESS SENT BACK WITH THE ENTIRE CREW TO THE USA ON COMPLETION OF THEIR TOUR DUTY FOR A 31 CITY WAR BOND TOUR.
